OL,3,C'I must abide by the rules', says
OL,4,CMetro Mayor MP on second job crackdown
OL,6,FThe West of England's Metro Mayor MP
OL,7,FDan Norris says he's "sad in some
OL,8,Fways" that he's not allowed to stand
OL,9,Ffor re-election but "like everybody
OL,10,Felse" must "abide by the rules".
OL,12,FAs part of a crackdown on MPs having
OL,13,Fsecond jobs, the new MP for North East
OL,14,FSomerset & Hanham will not be able to
OL,15,Fcontinue in his mayoral role when it's
OL,16,Fup for re-election in May.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
