OL,3,C'I must abide by the rules', says
OL,4,CMetro Mayor MP on second job crackdown
OL,6,FMr Norris spoke to ITV News in
OL,7,FScotland at Sir Keir Starmer's first-
OL,8,Fever meeting of his new Council of
OL,9,FNations and Regions on Friday 11
OL,10,FOctober.
OL,12,FMr Norris said: "Like everybody else,
OL,13,FI have to abide by the rules, and if
OL,14,Fthat's the rules, that's what happens."
OL,16,FThe Labour Party's National Executive
OL,17,FCommittee approved the rulebook
OL,18,Fchanges at the annual conference in
OL,19,FLiverpool earlier this month, saying
OL,20,Fit is "committed to MPs focusing on
OL,21,Fbeing MPs".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
