OL,3,C'I must abide by the rules', says
OL,4,CMetro Mayor MP on second job crackdown
OL,6,FAfter losing the former Wansdyke seat
OL,7,Fto Sir Jacob Rees-Mogg in 2010, Mr
OL,8,FNorris stood to be the Mayor of the
OL,9,FWest of England Combined Authority
OL,10,F(WECA) in 2021.
OL,12,FThis year, he beat Sir Jacob to win
OL,13,Fthe North East Somerset and Hanham
OL,14,Fseat, with a majority of 5,319.
OL,15,FShortly after winning, he said there
OL,16,Fwas "precedent in politics" for MPs to
OL,17,Fcarry out two jobs at the same time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
