OL,3,C'I must abide by the rules', says
OL,4,CMetro Mayor MP on second job crackdown
OL,6,FSpeaking in Edinburgh, Mr Norris said:
OL,7,F"We've got off to a really good start
OL,8,Fsince I've been Mayor, we've got a
OL,9,Fhigher profile, we're on the right
OL,10,Ftrajectory.
OL,12,F"I'm sad in some ways not to be able
OL,13,Fto continue that, but I know that
OL,14,Fhopefully the next Labour Mayor will
OL,15,Fbe able to continue that work and it's
OL,16,Fvery important for the people in my
OL,17,Farea who really ned to get growth and
OL,18,Fwealth creation going again, because
OL,19,Fit's been very absent for many years
OL,20,Fand that needs to change."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
