OL,3,C'I must abide by the rules', says
OL,4,CMetro Mayor MP on second job crackdown
OL,6,FLabour's group leader on Bristol City
OL,7,FCouncil, Tom Renhard, announced on
OL,8,FFriday that he is standing to be the
OL,9,FParty's candidate for the mayoral
OL,10,Felection next year.
OL,12,FIn a post on X, he said: "Everyone in
OL,13,Four region deserves the chance to
OL,14,Fthrive. Truly affordable homes,
OL,15,Fnature, infrastructure, buses under
OL,16,Fpublic control, community investment
OL,17,Fand good jobs.
OL,19,F"That's why I'm standing to be your
OL,20,FLabour candidate for West of England
OL,21,FMayor."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
