OL,3,C'I must abide by the rules', says
OL,4,CMetro Mayor MP on second job crackdown
OL,6,FMr Norris was joined in Edinburgh by
OL,7,Fthe prime minister and regional mayors
OL,8,Ffrom across the country, as the PM
OL,9,Freiterated his commitment to greater
OL,10,Fdevolution of powers to local leaders.
OL,12,FBut, as it stands, Mr Norris is the
OL,13,Fonly regional mayor in the South West
OL,14,Fof England, with councils across the
OL,15,Fregion currently in talks about
OL,16,Fpossible devolution deals.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
