OL,3,C'I must abide by the rules', says
OL,4,CMetro Mayor MP on second job crackdown
OL,6,FWhen asked if other parts of the South
OL,7,FWest should be pushing ahead with
OL,8,Fthem, Mr Norris said: "It's for each
OL,9,Farea to decide what it needs, it's not
OL,10,Ffor me to tell them.
OL,12,F"But what I know is it works very well
OL,13,Ffor my region."
OL,15,FSpeaking at the opening of the meeting
OL,16,Fon Friday morning, Sir Keir Starmer
OL,17,Fsaid the council was a "statement of
OL,18,Fintent on my behalf, and on behalf of
OL,19,Fthe government, about the way in which
OL,20,Fwe want to work with all of you.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
