OL,6,F"I think that is as important as the
OL,7,Fsubstance of what we discuss, is how
OL,8,Fwe collaborate, how we work together.
OL,10,F"Because the UK is really strong,
OL,11,Fwe've got so much to offer,
OL,12,Fparticularly when it comes to growth
OL,13,Fand investment, but we are a bit
OL,14,Fcomplicated."
